(63, '10001696', 'Pottery Wheels (Non Powered)', 'Includes any products that may be described/observed as a non-powered revolving wheel on which crafted pottery products are formed and shaped. Non-powered pottery wheels are typically foot operated.', 'Excludes products such as powered Pottery Wheels.', '2021-12-16 22:30:34', '2021-12-16 22:30:34'),
