(1810, '10007394', 'Unspecified Cloverplantsplants (Trifolium)', 'Includes any product that can be described/observed as the cultivated unharvested form of Unspecified cloverplantsplants, grown from species and varieties (cultivars) in the genus Trifolium not specified elsewhere, to be used as a forage, as feed for livestock, as green manure or as a covercrop. ', 'Specifically excludes harvested products from Unspecified cloverplantsplants and by-products such as Prepared/Processed or Unprepared/Unprocessed Unspecified cloverplants. EPPO Code: 1TRFG', '2021-12-16 22:30:36', '2021-12-16 22:30:36'),
