(1817, '10007408', 'Amaranth Feedplants (Amaranthus Spp.)', 'Includes any product that can be described/observed as the cultivated unharvested form of Amaranthplants, grown from various species and varieties (cultivars) in the genus Amaranthus spp. to be used as a forage, as feed for livestock, as green manure or as a covercrop. ', 'Specifically excludes harvested products from Amaranthplants and by-products such as Prepared/Processed or Unprepared/Unprocessed Amaranth. EPPO Code: 1AMAG', '2021-12-16 22:30:36', '2021-12-16 22:30:36'),
