(4990, '10002922', 'Exterior Appearance Accessories Other (Automotive)', 'Includes any products that can be described/observed as a covering, specifically designed to enhance the exterior appearance of the car, where the user of the schema is not able to classify the products in existing bricks within the schema.', 'Excludes all currently classified car exterior appearance products.', '2021-12-16 22:30:45', '2021-12-16 22:30:45'),
